<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>10350</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21148</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哈哈！” 杰克突然大笑起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21148</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>26808</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“五颗小豆子换一头大奶牛？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>26808</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>30889</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>老爷爷点了点头，也笑了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>30889</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39160</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“怎么样，杰克？”他问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39160</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41893</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克摇了摇头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41893</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44216</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不要！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44216</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>49230</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我才不会用米可换五颗小豆子呢！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>49230</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>54603</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>老爷爷耸了耸肩：“那算了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>54603</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>62049</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>虽然它们很小，但是它们是魔豆哦！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>62049</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77881</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>说完他就转身走了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77881</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83763</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“等等！”杰克大喊，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83763</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>88704</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你是说它们是……魔豆吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>88704</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>92285</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的。”老爷爷走回来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>92285</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>97220</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他又拿出了豆子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>97220</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>102938</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我……不知道……”杰克说得很慢。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>102938</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106772</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他盯着豆子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106772</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>110781</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后他又看了看米可。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>110781</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116096</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们卖掉米可是为了换钱。”杰克说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116096</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>122307</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“如果我用它换豆子，妈妈肯定会……”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>122307</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>127459</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你可以种下这些豆子。”老爷爷说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>127459</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135289</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“它们的豆茎会长啊长，一直长到天上！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135289</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>139123</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯……”杰克心想，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>139123</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145417</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“能长到天上的豆茎？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145417</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154183</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>听起来很有趣。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154183</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159722</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“给你！”老爷爷把豆子放到杰克手里，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159722</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161596</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“种下这些豆子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161596</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>178369</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>如果没有神奇的事情发生，我就把米可还给你。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>178369</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184485</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那就这样说好了！”杰克说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184485</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>190100</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快，老爷爷就牵着奶牛离开了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>190100</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>197930</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克也拿着五颗小豆子回家了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
